OL,3,CCardiff Bus staff vote to accept pay
OL,4,Coffer and call off strike action
OL,6,FCardiff Bus employees have called off
OL,7,Fa three-week and a half strike, after
OL,8,Faccepting a new pay offer.
OL,10,FUnite members had announced plans to
OL,11,Fwalk out over pay and conditions
OL,12,Fearlier this year. The proposed
OL,13,Findustrial action was set to begin on
OL,14,FTuesday, 2 September.
OL,16,FAfter receiving a revised offer from
OL,17,FCardiff Bus, the union paused the
OL,18,Fstrike to ballot members. On Friday,
OL,19,Fthey announced their members had voted
OL,20,Fto accept the offer and therefore the
OL,21,Fstrike action would be called off.
