OL,3,CCardiff Bus staff vote to accept pay
OL,4,Coffer and call off strike action
OL,6,FThe new agreement includes a 5.86%
OL,7,Fbackdated pay rise, improvements to
OL,8,Fsick pay and an additional five
OL,9,Fminutes walking time to guarantee a 45-
OL,10,Fminute break for drivers.
OL,12,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,13,Fsaid: "Our members at Cardiff Bus have
OL,14,Ffought to improve and protect pay and
OL,15,Fconditions not just for themselves,
OL,16,Fbut for the long-term benefit of the
OL,17,Fsector in Wales. This shows the power
OL,18,Fof a union, and the hardworking reps
OL,19,Fshould be applauded for their actions.
