OL,3,CCardiff Bus staff vote to accept pay
OL,4,Coffer and call off strike action
OL,6,F"This is yet another example of Unite
OL,7,Fwinning for workers up and down the
OL,8,Fcountry. We will always battle to
OL,9,Fimprove members' pay and conditions."
OL,11,FCraig Hampton-Stone, Managing Director
OL,12,Fat Cardiff Bus, said: "We are
OL,13,Fdelighted that this dispute has been
OL,14,Fresolved through constructive
OL,15,Fdialogue. The agreement reflects our
OL,16,Fdetermination to support our employees
OL,17,Fwhile ensuring Cardiff Bus continues
OL,18,Fto provide a reliable and dependable
OL,19,Fservice for our city.
